ce/diary/media/%E6%82%A0%E4%B9%85%E3%81%AE%E6%A3%AE%EF%BC%92.webp?w=160&amp;h=104 160w, https://images.microcms-assets.io/protected/ap-northeast-1:45600192-d42c-45d5-a8f8-dad14f377d3c/service/diary/media/%E6%82%A0%E4%B9%85%E3%81%AE%E6%A3%AE%EF%BC%92.webp?w=320&amp;h=208 320w, https://images.microcms-assets.io/protected/ap-northeast-1:45600192-d42c-45d5-a8f8-dad14f377d3c/service/diary/media/%E6%82%A0%E4%B9%85%E3%81%AE%E6%A3%AE%EF%BC%92.webp?w=640&amp;h=416 640w, https://images.microcms-assets.io/protected/ap-northeast-1:45600192-d42c-45d5-a8f8-dad14f377d3c/service/diary/media/%E6%82%A0%E4%B9%85%E3%81%AE%E6%A3%AE%EF%BC%92.webp?w=1280&amp;h=832 1280w\" sizes=\"80vw\" loading=\"lazy\"></picture><br>悠久の森２の紫コウモリが徘徊しているエリアです。<br>クリスタル（入り口方面）から３体目の木の奥です。</p><h1 id=\"h648f1c9cf1\">簡易ヒールのアイテム名</h1><p>癒やしのチョーカーというのがアクセサリーアイテム名です。<br><picture><source srcSet=\"https://images.microcms-assets.io/protected/ap-northeast-1:45600192-d42c-45d5-a8f8-dad14f377d3c/service/diary/media/%E7%99%92%E3%82%84%E3%81%97%E3%81%AE%E3%83%81%E3%83%A7%E3%83%BC%E3%82%AB%E3%83%BC.webp?w=80&amp;h=52&amp;fm=webp 80w, https://images.microcms-assets.io/protected/ap-northeast-1:45600192-d42c-45d5-a8f8-dad14f377d3c/service/diary/media/%E7%99%92%E3%82%84%E3%81%97%E3%81%AE%E3%83%81%E3%83%A7%E3%83%BC%E3%82%AB%E3%83%BC.webp?w=160&amp;h=104&amp;fm=webp 160w, https://images.microcms-assets.io/protected/ap-northeast-1:45600192-d42c-45d5-a8f8-dad14f377d3c/service/diary/media/%E7%99%92%E3%82%84%E3%81%97%E3%81%AE%E3%83%81%E3%83%A7%E3%83%BC%E3%82%AB%E3%83%BC.webp?w=320&amp;h=208&amp;fm=webp 320w, https://images.microcms-assets.io/protected/ap-northeast-1:45600192-d42c-45d5-a8f8-dad14f377d3c/service/diary/media/%E7%99%92%E3%82%84%E3%81%97%E3%81%AE%E3%83%81%E3%83%A7%E3%83%BC%E3%82%AB%E3%83%BC.webp?w=640&amp;h=416&amp;fm=webp 640w, https://images.microcms-assets.io/protected/ap-northeast-1:45600192-d42c-45d5-a8f8-dad14f377d3c/service/diary/media/%E7%99%92%E3%82%84%E3%81%97%E3%81%AE%E3%83%81%E3%83%A7%E3%83%BC%E3%82%AB%E3%83%